Yayo yose yotendigwa na Muhe imwe muhala iyo komgalila chila munhu viyolonda.
Fana viya lukuli lwa munhu ni lumwe, na viungo vingi va lukuli lwake, mbali viungo vingi va lukuli luno ni lukuli lumwe, ivo viya Chilisito iviya viyeli.
Kwaviya kwa Muhe iyo imwe muhala chila munhu kabatizigwa muladi yawe lukuli lumwe, hata fana Wayahudi hebu wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi, hata fana watumwa hebu wanhu weli bule, na cheye chose ching'wa Muhe iyo imwe muhala.
Mbali lukuli lwa munhu lukuli lwa chihande chimwe muhala, mbali lwa vihande vingi.
