Mbali Mulungu kalagusa chila chinhu muna lukuli, chila chinhu muna ulukolo fana viyalondile.
One yose yawile chiungo chimwe muhala, lukuli lukala kulihi?
Kwaviya mbali uhuwilo wako ni mwingi, mbali lukuli lwa munhu iyo imwe muhala.
Na ziso hadidaha bule kuulongela mkono, "Sipatile bule weye," wala ditwi hadidaha bule kuulongela magulu, "Sipatile bule weye."
